Chevron Employees Multipurpose Cooperative Society (CEMCS Ltd.) – The Society was first registered as Gulf Oil Employees Cooperative Society in 1966. It Changed name to Chevron Employees Cooperative Thrift and Credit Society Limited (CECT & CS LTD) in 1995 inline with the host company’s change management. It was Upgraded to Chevron Employees Multipurpose Cooperative Society (CEMCS Ltd) In 2006 to capture its increasing membership and business scope. We are currently recruiting to fill the position below: Location: Lekki, Lagos Human Resources: Learning and Development: Performance Management: Total Reward: Administration: Legal: Qualifications and Experience Application Closing Date26th June, 2020. The post Human Resources / Admin & Legal Manager at Chevron Employees Multipurpose Cooperative Society Limited (CEMCS Ltd.) appeared first on Jobs in Nigeria – http://jobsinnigeria.careers. Get all the Latest news, Breaking headlines,Sport, Education, Finance, Gists, Jobs, Music/Video, Technology and Top stories in real time in Nigeria and around the world.